nput\").props.value\n\tif sdate \u003d\u003d \u0027\u0027 or str(sdate).upper() \u003d\u003d \u0027None\u0027.upper():\n\t\tself.view.params.StartDate \u003d None\n\telse:\n\t\tself.view.params.StartDate \u003d self.parent.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntDate\").getChild(\"cntStart\").getChild(\"DateTimeInput\").props.value\n\t\t\n\tedate \u003d self.parent.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntDate\").getChild(\"cntEnd\").getChild(\"DateTimeInput\").props.value\n\tif edate \u003d\u003d \u0027\u0027 or str(edate).upper() \u003d\u003d \u0027None\u0027.upper():\n\t\tself.view.params.EndDate \u003d None\n\telse:\n\t\tself.view.params.EndDate \u003d self.parent.parent.parent.getChild(\"cntDate\").getChild(\"cntEnd\").getChild(\"DateTimeInput\").props.value\n\t"
